708018f-a.title: Manhattan: 3rd Avenue - 17th Street
708018f-a.text:
Third Avenue, north from and including 17th Street. At 190 Thirs Avenue, adjoining the N.W. corner of 17th Street, is the GermanAmerican Athletic Club, or Scheffel Hall, known for its popular
restaurant.
May 221, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
